title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

Convenient—includes useful features like a spell checker, calculator, calender with personal notes and a printing option. [From an advertisement for The MailStation, an email appliance. Submitted by Peter How, University Park, Florida.—It's only like a spell checker, or else it would have caught “calender.”]
